step.action:
Load scoring thresholds and weights from workflow config:
      - confident threshold = {score_threshold_confident}
      - partial threshold = {score_threshold_partial}
      - minimum repo coverage percent = {minimum_repo_coverage_percent}
      - weights = skills:{weight_skill_coverage}, understanding:{weight_project_understanding}, docs+ticketing:{weight_documentation_ticket_readiness}, testability:{weight_testability_readiness}, operability:{weight_operational_readiness}

Write Markdown report to {{confidence_report_md}} in {{document_language}}:

      # Project Understanding Confidence Report — {{date}}

      ## Verdict
      - Coverage gate: {{coverage_gate_failed ? "FAILED" : "PASSED"}}
      - Repo coverage: {{repo_coverage_percent}}%
      - Global score: {{global_confidence_score}} / 100 (raw: {{raw_global_confidence_score}})
      - Confidence level: {{confidence_verdict}}
      - Assistant mode: {{assistant_mode}}

      ## Repo Coverage Matrix
      {{repo_coverage_matrix}}

      ## Scoring Breakdown
      - Skill coverage: {{skill_coverage}} / 100 (weight {weight_skill_coverage}%)
      - Project understanding: {{project_understanding}} / 100 (weight {weight_project_understanding}%)
      - Documentation + ticket readiness: {{documentation_ticket_readiness}} / 100 (weight {weight_documentation_ticket_readiness}%)
      - Testability readiness: {{testability_readiness}} / 100 (weight {weight_testability_readiness}%)
      - Operational readiness: {{operational_readiness}} / 100 (weight {weight_operational_readiness}%)

      ## Understanding Proof
      {{for each repo: "what this repo does", key flows, and unknowns with file references}}

      ## Skill Fit Analysis
      {{required_skills vs available_capabilities with gaps}}

      ## Testing Readiness
      {{exact commands, prerequisites, and missing setup}}

      ## Critical Gaps (Blocking)
      {{critical_gaps}}

      ## Recommended Gaps (Non-blocking)
      {{recommended_gaps}}

      ## Prioritized User Action Backlog
      {{action_backlog}}

      ## Fast Confidence Boost Plan (+20 points)
      {{confidence_boost_plan}}

      ## Execution Repository
      - Mode: {{execution_repository_mode}}
      - Artifacts repo: {{confidence_artifact_repo_path}}
